This paper is about improving uncertainty estimates in deep ensembles, which is a topic that falls under the broad category of machine learning. Specifically, the paper focuses on neural networks and their performance on out-of-distribution test examples. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.CV (Computer Vision), cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing), and cs.SY (Systems and Control).
